00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,560
His work is tough and his schedule is tight.

586
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:10,560
And he also works too hard.

587
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:12,440
Your brother is an innate workaholic.

588
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,920
So, how have you been doing?

589
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:17,920
Good.

590
00:31:20,840 --> 00:31:21,720
Ren,

591
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:23,840
you've grown taller and stronger.

592
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,720
At least you know you need to come back.

593
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:29,760
Someone has been missing you like crazy,

594
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,160
but he's too shy to tell you that.

595
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:33,240
Instead, he can only throw a tantrum.

596
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,040
What can we do?

597
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:36,040
He's 14 now, going through a rebellious phase!

598
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,200
A rebellious phase!

599
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:43,840
Ren,

600
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,400
it happened to be your 10th birthday

601
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:47,360
the last time I came back.

602
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:49,760
Mei Xing, did you miss me?

603
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,120
Of course I did.

604
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:53,560
Let's go.

605
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,480
How have you been doing?

606
00:31:57,560 --> 00:31:58,760
How's your studies?

607
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,160
Same old.

608
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,240
Not bad.

609
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,360
Since you are back,

610
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,160
I want to ask you

611
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,320
a few questions.

612
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,280
My mom told me you'd come.

613
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,080
I thought it was a lie.

614
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,680
When I called you last month,

615
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:12,880
you didn't mention anything

616
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,000
about coming to Zhenjiang.

617
00:32:14,680 --> 00:32:15,280
I didn't say anything

618
00:32:15,320 --> 00:32:16,120
because I was afraid you'd be upset

619
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:16,800
if I couldn't make it.

620
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,520
I wouldn't be upset.

621
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,480
But I'd be disappointed for a couple of days.

622
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,560
Really? Just a couple of days?

623
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:24,960
When you were little, it'd usually

624
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,240
take you at least a week to forgive me!

625
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,920
It's way in the past!

626
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:29,040
Can't believe you're still bringing it up!

627
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:30,440
I'm not petty.

628
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:31,320
I just vividly remember it.

629
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:32,880
You are my only sister.

630
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:33,680
Of course I won't forget it.

631
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:35,840
Let's go.

632
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:46,960
You didn't eat much at dinner.

633
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,560
Don't like the food?

634
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:50,880
It was a long trip.

635
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:54,960
Your younger brother will get married before you do.

636
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:55,880
I'm not

637
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:57,880
so happy about this.

638
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:01,000
The girl I love hasn't showed up yet. It can't be forced.

639
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:03,760
Mom, Chen has just come back

640
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:04,760
and changed his clothes,

641
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,679
but you're already nagging him about getting married.

642
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,080
He'd be even more reluctant to come back in the future.

643
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,040
I said that only because

644
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:10,040
he rarely comes back.

645
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,440
Since you are home now,

646
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:13,040
you should set a date for your wedding.

647
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:15,679
I hope you can get married in May.

648
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:18,280
I'll make my own

649
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,960
decisions about my marriage.

650
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:24,120
Mom, I'm the one who'll get married in April.

651
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,760
Would you think of me and Jiaren first?

652
00:34:28,159 --> 00:34:29,560
Are you trying to help

653
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:30,560
your brother out?

654
00:34:32,159 --> 00:34:33,560
You are not the only one who wants to see my brother.

655
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,480
My uncles are all waiting to see him too.

656
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,920
Chen, let's go.

657
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,360
I'll take my leave then.

658
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:41,520
Fine.

659
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,960
Have a chat with mom.

660
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:47,240
She's so concerned about my brother's engagement

661
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,320
that she had forgotten about you.

662
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:54,360
Come here.

663
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:01,640
Mom.

664
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,760
Uncle.

665
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:14,640
Chen.

666
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:17,400
It's good

667
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,280
to have you back!

668
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:23,120
Uncles, thank you

669
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:24,200
for coming here!

670
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:26,120
You are finally home.

671
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,360
Of course we'd come to see you

672
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:28,560
even if there's nothing important.

673
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:30,960
Don't just stand there.

674
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:31,840
Sit down.

675
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:32,560
Please.

676
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,080
Chen, take a seat.

677
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:34,720
Okay.

678
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:43,440
Before I came back,

679
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:45,080
I'd been working on something.

680
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:47,760
I think you've all heard of it.

681
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:49,920
We have.

682
00:35:50,120 --> 00:35:51,120
It's an investment meeting, right?

683
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:52,160
It's a good thing.

684
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,480
Yea.

685
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:54,800
But

686
00:35:55,040 --> 00:35:56,240
no one here has stated their position on

687
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:57,840
whether you'd join or not.

688
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:21,040
Why are you all looking at me?

689
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:23,280
Chen is the future head

690
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,560
of this family.

691
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,000
You should all

692
00:36:26,240 --> 00:36:27,520
listen to him.

693
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:28,360
Right?

694
00:36:33,640 --> 00:36:34,560
In recent years,

695
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,840
we've been

696
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:37,680
investing in overseas projects,

697
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:39,520
like buying properties

698
00:36:39,720 --> 00:36:41,160
and utility companies.

699
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:42,480
This has already shaken

700
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:43,920
the foundation of our family business.

701
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:45,680
For generations,

702
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:47,480
our family

703
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,320
has always had our foundations

704
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,840
rooted in the national industries

705
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,360
no matter

706
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,920
in times of prosperity or decline.

707
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,280
The key purpose for next month's

708
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,600
investment meeting

709
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,040
is to attract investors

710
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:06,240
to develop the domestic manufacturing sector.

711
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:08,520
As the host of the meeting,

712
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,360
we'll announce then that we are going

713
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,640
to redirect our investment funds

714
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:14,040
to domestic manufacturing.

715
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:16,280
That's why I hope I can

716
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,760
get your

717
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:19,560
full support.

718
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:31,040
Chen,

719
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:32,880
you've just come back.

720
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:34,680
There's no rush.

721
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,160
Take it slow.

722
00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:38,840
Okay?

723
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:39,840
Yeah.

724
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,880
You just came back. Have some rest.

725
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:43,720
Regarding this matter,

726
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:46,480
it won't be too late to make a decision

727
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,920
until you and your uncle reach an agreement.

728
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:49,280
Exactly!

729
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,320
Since we've made a public announcement

730
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,160
that we'll hold an investment meeting,

731
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,720
then we must go through with it.

732
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,600
Moreover,

733
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:59,080
this is the first thing that Chen

734
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:00,640
is doing after coming back.

735
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:02,240
I, for one, will give

736
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,480
my full support.

737
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:07,560
However,

738
00:38:07,720 --> 00:38:08,560
this meeting seems

739
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,000
more of a show

740
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:12,360
than of substance for our family.

741
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:16,760
Chen, you've just come back.

742
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,280
Take some rest first.

743
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,920
Some decisions

744
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,280
can't be made

745
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,400
overnight.

746
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:28,840
Take a rest first.

747
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:48,920
Do you believe in reincarnation?

748
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,160
We knew each other

749
00:39:54,040 --> 00:39:55,320
in our past lives.

750
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,560
Where are we going?

751
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:25,160
Uncle Lin,

752
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:26,840
how long does it take to drive

753
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,120
from here to Shanghai?

754
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,280
Driving during the night would take longer.

755
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:30,560
Four hours.

756
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:33,360
We'd get to Shanghai at about 11:00 p.m.

757
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:35,240
Let's go to Shanghai.

758
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,160
Right now?

759
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:38,040
Yes.

760
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:38,920
For work?

761
00:40:38,500 --> 00:41:06,740
[Family of Books and Ritual]

762
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:41,840
To meet a friend.

763
00:40:43,160 --> 00:40:44,480
You have a friend in Shanghai?

764
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:46,960
Let's go.

765
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:14,660
[Starting a business is like drinking. Set your dream free.]

766
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,560
Food is here!

