00:41:14,660 --> 00:41:23,020
[Recording Studio]

768
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,320
Director Wang, you came!

769
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,520
I knew when you guys would be here!

770
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:20,000
Come on! Let's eat!

771
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:20,560
Come!

772
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:22,920
Here.

773
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:25,700
["Drunk in Love"   The Lost Romance]

774
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,040
Shi Yi.

775
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:27,480
Well...

776
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,840
If you don't like the food,

777
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:30,280
I can bring you to another place.

778
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:32,960
Miss Shi, your phone.

779
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:33,600
Thanks!

