782
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:38,640
All right. I'll go make a phone call.

783
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:40,840
Thank you, Director Wang!

784
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:41,840
Thank you!

785
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:42,760
Cut it out!

786
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,320
Hello?

787
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:03,440
Who is this?

788
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,480
It's me, Zhousheng Chen.

789
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,680
Oh! It's you!

790
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:13,080
Have you finished work?

791
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:17,320
Just. That's why I missed your call.

792
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,080
It's all right.

793
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:22,720
If you have time,

794
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:24,480
would you like to have supper with me?

795
00:42:25,480 --> 00:42:26,480
Sure. Where?

796
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:28,320
Tell me your address.

797
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,240
I'll go pick you up.

798
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:30,560
It's okay.

799
00:42:30,720 --> 00:42:31,840
You can send me the address of the restaurant.

800
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:33,240
I'll meet you there.

801
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,880
Let me pick you up.

802
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:37,840
Okay.

803
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:38,680
I'll send you

804
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:39,920
my address in a bit.

805
00:42:41,040 --> 00:42:41,520
Okay.

806
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:43,320
I'll let you know when I'm there.

807
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:44,680
Bye-bye.

808
00:43:04,820 --> 00:43:08,460
[Recording Studio]

809
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:11,640
Are you okay?

810
00:43:14,240 --> 00:43:14,920
I'm fine.

811
00:43:17,520 --> 00:43:20,360
You look so different!

812
00:43:23,680 --> 00:43:25,200
Because of the suit?

813
00:43:27,520 --> 00:43:27,960
This is what I

814
00:43:28,120 --> 00:43:28,920
usually wear when I'm

815
00:43:29,120 --> 00:43:30,320
not at the institute.

816
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:32,080
Does it bug you?

817
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:33,640
Not at all!

818
00:43:33,840 --> 00:43:34,440
It fits you perfectly!

819
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:41,080
Why did you insist on picking me up?

820
00:43:43,960 --> 00:43:46,080
Well, it's already midnight

821
00:43:46,720 --> 00:43:48,360
and you don't have any security guards here.

822
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:49,480
I was concerned

823
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:50,520
about your safety.

824
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:58,240
Let's go then.

825
00:44:20,320 --> 00:44:22,400
Miss Shi Yi. Nice to meet you!

826
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:23,920
You, too!

827
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:29,160
Is this your car?

828
00:44:30,840 --> 00:44:31,640
Please get in.

829
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:38,560
Thanks!

830
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:19,040
The job this time is quite nice.

831
00:45:19,280 --> 00:45:20,680
They even assigned a driver and a car for him.

832
00:45:31,440 --> 00:45:33,240
Should I say something?

833
00:45:43,880 --> 00:45:44,800
Did you

834
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:46,640
meet someone important before this?

835
00:45:48,480 --> 00:45:49,480
A few elders.

836
00:46:04,840 --> 00:46:05,880
How come he always gives

837
00:46:06,040 --> 00:46:06,920
short responses

838
00:46:07,120 --> 00:46:08,400
that leads to nowhere?

839
00:46:10,240 --> 00:46:11,680
What a weirdo!

840
00:46:12,040 --> 00:46:14,040
Lucky for you, I don't mind that!
